@cindex bind

These 2 scripts mount and unmount both cvsroot and cache directories 
into the chroot jail, using the bind option (see @code{man 8 mount}).
It allow @activityServer{} to respectively enable/disable remote 
meta-data upgrades and data copies when starting/stoping,
without beeing setuid @code{root}.

